  "title": "Customer Service Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Oversee field service, service centre, and outsourced call centre operations to ensure smooth daily operations</p></li><li><p>Manage and lead service teams to maintain service quality, productivity, and customer satisfaction.</p></li><li><p>Monitor SLAs and KPIs, resolve operational issues, and improve service efficiency</p></li><li><p>Identify process gaps and drive continuous improvement initiatives</p></li><li><p>Support development and implementation of service policies, procedures, and KPIs</p></li><li><p>Prepare and review service performance and cost reports</p></li><li><p>Handle escalated customer complaints and service disputes, ensuring proper investigation and resolution</p></li><li><p>Support mediation or legal cases by preparing service records when required</p></li><li><p>Any other adhoc duties as assigned<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma in related fields</p></li><li><p>Min 5 years experience in customer service management</p></li><li><p>Experience in IT or Consumer Electronics industry is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Location: Jurong East</p></li><li><p>Working Hours: Mon - Fri, alternate Sat</p></li><li><p>Salary: Up to $6000<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>How to apply:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants kindly state your expected salary, last drawn salary and starting date.</p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Log on to www.e-cruitteam.com.sg for more job opportunities!<br /></p><p>EA Personnel: Teo Kai Xin, Joey</p><p>EA Reg ID: R23114229</p><p>EA Licence No.:19C9603</p>",
