    "description": "<p>E-Cruit Team is a reputable and trusted recruitment agency committed to delivering effective staffing solutions to both individuals and organisations with urgency and dedication.<br>\n<br>\nFounded with the vision of providing a specialised, high-quality recruitment experience, E-Cruit Team takes pride in offering a personalised and professional approach to every hiring need.<br>\n<br>\nWith a team of experienced consultants, we bring deep local recruitment expertise and market understanding to the table. This enables us to connect top talent with the right opportunities — efficiently and effectively.<br>\n<br>\nWhether you’re an employer looking to build a reliable workforce or a candidate seeking the right job fit, E-Cruit Team is here to support you every step of the way.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our services includes:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Local Recruitment (Permanent)&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Contract and temporary staffing (Temp &amp; Contract)&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Various work pass application</li>\n  <li>Event Support Manpower solutions&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Payroll services</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>E-Cruit Team, Recruit with confidence!</p>",
